{
  "stem": "2170.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I was trying to open up the door and go out to look, like, 10 o'clock at night, it was snowing, and I wanted to see if everything is quiet.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As I opened the door, I saw two Ukrainian policemen with their guns, already circling around our house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I knew something will happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The whole night, I-- at that time, somehow I always try to sleep at my sister's house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother, my other sisters, and my other brothers slept in their house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I did not see them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I always wanted to be close to my sister, so I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As we saw already, at night, in the middle of the night was very quiet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had a feeling that tomorrow we going to die, because we knew that the police surrounded our house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we cannot run no more, and this what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Across our door lived a Jewish woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was married to a Gentile, a Russian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had two little daughters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her husband was in the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she came in, and she said to us, what's going to happen to us?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she mentioned even whatever happens, maybe her children will be safe, because they're half-Jewish, because their father is not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At 5:00 in the morning, it was quiet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was Christmas. 6 o'clock in the morning was already light a little bit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the snow was coming down very quiet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew something will happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After 6:00, like 7 o'clock, we heard already from the center of the town, shooting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then all of a sudden, I'm looking out from the window, and I see running two Germans and one of the head of the Ukrainian police, Baranchuck, with two guns in his hands.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
